      "status": "todo",
      "title": "Investigate upstream wait --download file persistence semantics",
      "description": "While validating RQ-0032 against agent-browser 0.26.0, the wrapper received a successful wait --download result with data.path/savedFilePath matching the requested path, but the requested local file was not present on disk immediately afterward in this environment. This is independent of the wrapper presentation work, which now renders and forwards the observed upstream saved-file metadata. Determine whether upstream expects a different fixture pattern, download directory configuration, or has a saveAs/persistence bug; then update the real-upstream contract test and docs to assert actual file existence when the upstream behavior is confirmed reliable.",
